        <item>
        <title>Notion Next.js &amp; Vercel搭建半自动博客</title>
        <link>https://lemoe.cn/blog/notion-next-js-vercel%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%8D%8A%E8%87%AA%E5%8A%A8%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/</link>
        <pubDate>Mon, 11 Apr 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
        
        <guid>https://lemoe.cn/blog/notion-next-js-vercel%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%8D%8A%E8%87%AA%E5%8A%A8%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/</guid>
        <description>&lt;img src="https://lemoe.cn/blog/notion-next-js-vercel%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%8D%8A%E8%87%AA%E5%8A%A8%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/header.png" alt="Featured image of post Notion Next.js &amp; Vercel搭建半自动博客" /&gt;&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;👀 辣眼睛提醒：本文没有适配夜间&lt;strong&gt;模式&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;概览&#34;&gt;概览
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;实例（没错就是本站）：&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://0wo.top/&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;猴子打字机产物 (0wo.top)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;准备材料&#34;&gt;准备材料：
&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;一个&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://github.com/&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;GitHub&lt;/a&gt;账号&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;一个&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://www.notion.so/&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;Notion&lt;/a&gt;账号&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;使用Github登录&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://vercel.com/&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;vercel&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;一个域名（如果有）&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;开始&#34;&gt;开始
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id=&#34;notion新建一页&#34;&gt;Notion新建一页
&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/a103840d-6f4f-43c8-8ba3-978275252707/09c69e23-74c8-45e9-884b-7449d440ac10/Untitled.png?X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;amp;X-Amz-Content-Sha256=UNSIGNED-PAYLOAD&amp;amp;X-Amz-Credential=AKIAT73L2G45GO43JXI4%2F20241111%2Fus-west-2%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;amp;X-Amz-Date=20241111T120915Z&amp;amp;X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;amp;X-Amz-Signature=57b6144478d4e7451303f4071842d31f3faee79873caf27198e78bfec3b9293f&amp;amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;amp;x-id=GetObject&#34;
	
	
	
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;公开并复制URL，保留最后的Page Id，如”18330b7d58314c368ede9d641f36c1cf”&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;fork&#34;&gt;Fork
&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;前往&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://github.com/transitive-bullshit/nextjs-notion-starter-kit&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;https://github.com/transitive-bullshit/nextjs-notion-starter-kit&lt;/a&gt; ，Fork一个副本（本站为&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://github.com/TennousuAthena/nextjs-notion&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;https://github.com/TennousuAthena/nextjs-notion&lt;/a&gt;）&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/a103840d-6f4f-43c8-8ba3-978275252707/3989ada4-df53-43bd-8aeb-78bc5a2b89fb/Untitled.png?X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;amp;X-Amz-Content-Sha256=UNSIGNED-PAYLOAD&amp;amp;X-Amz-Credential=AKIAT73L2G45GO43JXI4%2F20241111%2Fus-west-2%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;amp;X-Amz-Date=20241111T120915Z&amp;amp;X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;amp;X-Amz-Signature=1309782d33d987fb038b21d8eb73b2b9746ccf44f4b33335e64f5c60f77111cd&amp;amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;amp;x-id=GetObject&#34;
	
	
	
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;配置&#34;&gt;配置
&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;编辑&lt;code&gt;/**site.config.ts**&lt;/code&gt;，示例如下（请以您的项目文件为准）&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;
&lt;table class=&#34;lntable&#34;&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&#34;lntd&#34;&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt; 1
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt; 2
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt; 3
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt; 4
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt; 5
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt; 6
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt; 7
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt; 8
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt; 9
